  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c275b351&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FV08icaMk7MVakxaHkUQdLsZVXZVYUsrnYMFQsLA8uVUssnRSX8t0KjuC5tqAvdfHqULiaaWpNbBWhfGMB6Ojw4Nw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"Web3天空之城\" data-alias=\"Web3SkyCity\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/V08icaMk7MVbppLs8UnGYAUOJELEkxfo0QxOGhP1zvKpjV4X5c6nHQibuV79E4RgCqQeP4VDEAeiaPeQ6wI5QWRHQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"美好的，有趣的，值得铭记的\" data-id=\"MzIxODUzNTg2MA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Web3天空之城·城主：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在人工智能的演进版图中，一个长期以来的圣杯是：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI能否超越模仿和模式匹配，展现出真正的“技术创造力”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">？DeepMind的最新突破——自主编码代理AlphaEvolve——正为这个问题提供了一个肯定的、且极具冲击力的答案。这个由Pushmit Kohli和Matei等顶尖研究人员开发的系统，已经证明AI不仅能编写代码，更能发现和创造出超越人类数十年研究成果的全新算法。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这并非又一个代码补全工具。AlphaEvolve已在矩阵乘法等基础科学领域取得了超人成就，其发现的优化算法已被实际部署于谷歌的核心基础设施中。它让人联想起AlphaGo那颠覆围棋认知的“第37手”，标志着AI正从一个执行者，转变为一个能够拓展人类知识边界的发现者。在这次深度对话中，我们揭示了AlphaEvolve的工作原理，探讨了AI递归式自我完善的初步迹象，并展望了它将如何重塑未来的科学研究范式。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">核心观点摘要</span></strong></h3>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于AI的创造力本质：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“通过人工智能，我们确实能够进入算法的超人区域，而这是我们人类自己无法发现的……这证明了这些基于大规模神经网络的系统能够在这些大型搜索空间中进行推理和非常高效的探索。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于其核心工作机制：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“它结合了大型语言模型的创造力，以提出改进该解决方案的创造性新方法；用户提供的评估函数的严格性，它能够真正地从无效的事物中筛选出有效的事物；然后，它被包裹在一个进化算法中。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于其发现的价值：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们都有意选择了那些由最优秀的人长期研究的问题……通过拥有像AlphaEvolve这样的系统，能够在这些问题上发现新的东西，我认为这是我可以想象到的最强有力的证明，证明这确实是新的东西。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于递归式自我完善：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们可能看到了自我改进的初步迹象……它（AlphaEvolve）是加速下一代Gemini模型的训练。所以反馈循环相当长……但你可以肯定地称之为自我改进。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于未来人机协作的范式：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“你可以把它看作是一种工具，它将赋予科学家们一种超能力，使他们能够在非常复杂，有时甚至是违反直觉的解决方案空间中进行搜索。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于AI发现的独特价值：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“通常算法实际上比解决方案本身更有价值，因为算法会告诉你如何构建解决方案。这意味着你理解构建该解决方案所涉及的思路是什么。”</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">从AlphaGo到AlphaEvolve：对算法创造力的探索</span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve的诞生，源于DeepMind一个一以贯之的核心命题：如果AI能在一个庞大的博弈空间（如围棋）中找到人类未曾想过的制胜策略，那么它是否也能在同样浩瀚的“算法空间”中，发现更优的计算方法？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这个想法的首次验证是2022年的AlphaTensor。它针对计算机科学的基础算子——矩阵乘法，发现了50多年来超越人类数学家（如Strassen）的更优算法。这首次证明，AI有能力进入</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">算法的超人区域</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。但AlphaTensor是为特定问题设计的专用系统。AlphaEvolve的目标则更为宏大：构建一个</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">更通用的、能直接在程序代码空间中进行搜索的AI代理</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">我们问自己一个问题，如果你有一个智能体可以在围棋领域进行非常高效的搜索，为什么你不能使用同样的理念来搜索算法空间中的算法？</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Pushmit Kohli解释道。正是这种理念的迁移，促使团队开发出AlphaEvolve，一个利用大型语言模型（LLM）和进化搜索，在更广泛问题上进行探索的系统。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">工作原理：进化搜索与LLM创造力的结合</span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve的核心机制，是一套优雅结合了创造性与严谨性的自动化流程。用户首先需要定义问题，即提供一个</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">评估函数</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（evaluation function）。这个函数能精确判断任何一个被提出的解决方案的好坏。例如，在优化数据中心调度的问题上，评估函数可以是一个能模拟不同调度算法效率的模拟器。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">系统启动后，便进入一个进化循环：</span></p>\n  <ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: none;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">创造性提议</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：利用大型语言模型（如Gemini）的创造力，对现有的最优代码方案提出修改建议或全新的思路。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">2.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">严格评估</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：将LLM生成的新代码方案放入“评估函数”中进行严格测试，筛选出真正有效、性能更优的方案。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">进化迭代</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：将通过评估的优秀方案保留在一个多样化的“种群池”中，不断进行交叉、变异和迭代，确保搜索不会过早陷入局部最优。</span></p></li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“它结合了大型语言模型的创造力……用户提供的评估函数的严格性……然后，它被包裹在一个进化算法中，该算法确保我们能够探索该区域内算法的整个空间，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Matei如此总结。这个系统能够智能地适应问题的难度，对于简单问题能快速收敛，而对于“已经存在了几十年”的科学难题，它也能通过长时间的持续迭代，最终突破瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">递归式自我完善的黎明？</span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve最引人深思的一点，是它展现了</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">递归式自我完善</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的初步可能。在实验中，AlphaEvolve成功地发现并优化了用于训练其自身（及下一代Gemini模型）的算法，带来了23%的训练加速。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们可能看到了自我改进的初步迹象，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Matei谨慎地表示，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“你可以肯定地称之为自我改进。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;尽管他强调，这与能够无限累积、指数级增长的“硬起飞”式自我完善仍有距离，但这无疑是通往该方向的坚实一步。它证明了AI已经可以优化其自身的学习和计算效率。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">未来的关键问题在于，这种自我完善能否从计算效率层面，延伸到认知能力层面。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“你能不能改进训练过程，使得底层模型不仅训练速度更快，而且在某些认知任务中实际上从根本上更好？”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Pushmit提出了这个开放性问题。他认为，只要能构建出有效的评估函数来判断认知能力的提升，理论上没有理由做不到这一点。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">重塑科研范式：AI作为科学家的“超能力”</span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve的出现，预示着科学发现的范式即将发生根本性转变。研究人员认为，AI将成为科学家强大的协作工具，而非替代品。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“你可以把它看作是一种工具，它将赋予科学家们一种超能力，使他们能够在非常复杂，有时甚至是违反直-直觉的解决方案空间中进行搜索。”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个新范式中，人类科学家的角色将更多地转向更高层次的抽象工作：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: none;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">问题定义</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：精确地定义问题，并构建出能够量化“好坏”的评估函数。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">设定约束</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：为AI的搜索提供先验知识和约束条件，例如在药物发现中，不仅要有效，还要保证低毒性和可行的递送机制。</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">协作解读</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：AI的产出是可解释的代码，而非黑箱的神经网络。科学家可以审查、理解这些由AI发现的、充满新颖思路的算法，并从中获得深刻的洞见。</span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Matei强调，这种协作体验远超预期。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“通常算法实际上比解决方案本身更有价值，因为算法会告诉你如何构建解决方案。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;数学家们在与AlphaEvolve合作时，往往对其发现的算法结构本身更感兴趣，因为那揭示了解决问题的全新思路，这正是推进基础科学理解的核心。</span></p>\n  <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：一扇通往未知算法宇宙的大门 | 全文传送</span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">AlphaEvolve的意义，远不止于一个更强大的编码工具。它是一个发现引擎，一个能够系统性地探索人类因认知局限而未能触及的庞大算法空间的探路者。正如Pushmit所说，它就像一种人类发现的**“非常有趣的新元素”**，而最令人兴奋的是，观察富有创造力的人类将如何利用这种新元素去解决世界上最重要的问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">通过将LLM的创造力与进化算法的系统性搜索相结合，DeepMind不仅为解决当下的计算难题提供了新思路，更为重要的是，它为我们打开了一扇通往未知算法宇宙的大门。未来，人与AI的协作，将不再仅仅是使用工具，而是共同站在知识的前沿，向着更深邃的科学真理迈进。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&amp;mid=2247488651&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=065bd02423f3d36eb4553cc1fe1baad0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【全文版】深入AlphaEvolve：AI的创造力与自我完善之路\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【全文版】深入AlphaEvolve：AI的创造力与自我完善之路</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepMind 的 AlphaEvolve 通过结合 LLM 和进化算法，在矩阵乘法等领域发现超越人类的新算法，并展现出优化自身训练算法带来 23%加速的自我完善能力",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepMind 的 AlphaEvolve 通过结合 LLM 和进化算法，在矩阵乘法等领域发现超越人类的新算法，并展现出优化自身训练算法带来 23%加速的自我完善能力",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 DeepMind 开发的自主编码代理 AlphaEvolve，该系统结合了大型语言模型(LLM)的创造力和进化算法的严格评估，通过用户定义的评估函数在算法空间中发现超越人类研究的新算法。作为 AlphaTensor 的后继系统，AlphaEvolve 在矩阵乘法等基础科学领域取得了超人成就，并展现出递归式自我完善的初步迹象——优化自身训练算法带来 23%的加速。文章深入探讨了其工作原理、对科研范式的潜在影响，以及未来科学家将更多专注于问题定义和结果解读的人机协作新模式。",
